caption.p: The expression of genes associated with antioxidant defense response in fatty acid-induced HepG2 cells incubated with the tested honeys after 24 h. Results are mean ± SD of four replicates; *: p < 0.05 vs. control and #: p < 0.05 vs. fatty acid-treated cells, analyzed by one-way ANOVA followed by Duncan’s multiple comparison test. ( A): Analogue, ( B): manuka; ( C): arjuna, ( D): guggul, ( E): jiaogulan, ( F): olive honey. CT: Control without fatty acid and honey, FA: 1 mM fatty acid treatment, FAH1: 1 mM fatty acid and 1.0% honey; FAH2: 1 mM fatty acid and 2.0% honey ( w/ v).
